# Optional: ignore binary dumps (keep only if needed)
# -------------------------
#*.bin
#*.data

# -------------------------
# KEEP THESE (DO NOT IGNORE)
# -------------------------
# .ipynb
# .py
# .sql
# .txt
# .csv
# .xlsx
# .json
# .yml
# .md
# .png / .jpg / .jpeg / .gif
# .wav / .mp3
# .npy / .npz / .parquet / .pkl